HEADWORD: Bannerol
<hw>Ban"ner*ol</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A banderole; esp.
a banner displayed at a funeral procession and set over the tomb. See
<er>Banderole</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

